00095 #define Set_VECTOR_LENGTH       (8*32)  /* 8*32 elements */
00096 #define Set_VARRAY_SIZE         8
00097 #define Set_VECTOR_SIZE         8       /* 8 _32bit entries */
00098 #define Set_INDEX(x)            (x & 0x0FF)     /* extract lower 8 bits */
00099 #define Set_BASE(x)             (x >> 8)        /* discard lower 8 bits */
00100 #define Set_CONSTRUCT_BASE(x)   (x << 8)
00101 #define Set_WORD_SELECT(x)      (x >> 5 )       /* x / 32 */
00102 #define Set_BIT_SELECT(x)       (x & 0x01F)     /* extract lower 5 bits */
